quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  18,62,"Falamma jawaza qalalifatahu atina ghadaana laqadlaqeena min safarina hatha nasaba"
  18,63,"Qala araayta ith awaynaila assakhrati fa-innee naseetu alhootawama ansaneehu illa ashshaytanuan athkurahu wattakhatha sabeelahu fee albahriAAajaba"
  18,64,"Qala thalika ma kunnanabghi fartadda AAala atharihimaqasasa"
  18,65,"Fawajada AAabdan min AAibadinaataynahu rahmatan min AAindinawaAAallamnahu min ladunna AAilma"
  18,66,"Qala lahu moosa halattabiAAuka AAala an tuAAallimani mimma AAullimtarushda"
  18,67,"Qala innaka lan tastateeAAamaAAiya sabra"
  18,68,"Wakayfa tasbiru AAala malam tuhit bihi khubra"
  18,69,"Qala satajidunee in shaa Allahusabiran wala aAAsee laka amra"
  18,70,"Qala fa-ini ittabaAAtanee falatas-alnee AAan shay-in hatta ohditha lakaminhu thikra"
  18,71,"Fantalaqa hattaitha rakiba fee assafeenati kharaqahaqala akharaqtaha litughriqa ahlaha laqadji/ta shay-an imra"
  18,72,"Qala alam aqul innaka lan tastateeAAamaAAiya sabra"
  18,73,"Qala la tu-akhithneebima naseetu wala turhiqnee min amree AAusra"
  18,74,"Fantalaqa hattaitha laqiya ghulaman faqatalahu qalaaqatalta nafsan zakiyyatan bighayri nafsin laqad ji/ta shay-annukra"
